        "6d10740f-f585-407b-ac7d-cec6189d36bb": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>Q: How do you incorporate fashion and style into your daily life?</strong></p><p><br/></p><p>A: In the case of BBody barre, in the sportswear that I wear to class and, mainly, at the events where I am present with the brand, in athleisure style mode. On a personal level, I love to alternate between a very relaxed style to go to work in front of the sea, just as I love to get ready for a fancy dinner with friends.</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        }
      },
